Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:34.21,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,陛下 臣有事相禀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:35.20,Default,Hartgen,0,0,0,,讲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:36.96,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,是 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:39.06,Default,Arina,0,0,0,,怎么 有话快说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:43.69,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,六国联合方面 对我等召集军士一事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:46.21,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,已经发来书简质问缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:47.82,Default,Hartgen,0,0,0,,这又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:51.93,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,臣以为 武艺大会还是中止为妙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:54.80,Default,Arina,0,0,0,,啊？居然出此胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.29,Default,Hartgen,0,0,0,,为何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:02:00.48,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,<以命相搏>的规则恐已超出大会范畴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:04.21,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,而且 给优胜者的奖品…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:06.64,Default,Hartgen,0,0,0,,贾兹皇帝的遗体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:07.69,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:14.09,Default,Hartgen,0,0,0,,不论开展武艺大会 还是拿讨伐皇帝的战利品当奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,都是无可非议之事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:16.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:22.07,Default,Arina,0,0,0,,如此盛大的祭典 找遍菲尔比斯特大陆也难有第二个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:25.92,Default,Arina,0,0,0,,居然说中止 太可惜了啊 父王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:29.48,Default,Irina,0,0,0,,您打算如何处理呢 父王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:32.33,Default,Hartgen,0,0,0,,艾琳娜 伊琳娜 不必慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:34.30,Default,Hartgen,0,0,0,,武艺大会不会中止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:41.00,Title,,0,0,0,,疯狂之城
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:00.05,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,收获 非常非常有限
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.54,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.33,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,点个火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:05.67,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,惊人 大量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:07.67,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,旋转吧 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.71,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,<焚烧者>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.59,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,海产品 丰富
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.28,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,差不多行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.55,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,能吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:22.66,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,想要？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:23.51,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:24.55,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,那给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:25.41,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,受领
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.27,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,她吃东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.65,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不是魔法思念料也能吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:34.29,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,生物组织 营养 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:35.45,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,她不是机械的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:39.74,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,妮娃的身体 大概弃兽的身体组织 使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.12,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你小子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.38,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,被你们拿到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:50.76,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你知道这家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.21,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,你猜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:55.76,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,我即便知道 也不必告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:58.47,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 有隐情 回答 请求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:03:59.92,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:01.88,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我真身 什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.27,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,你不是早就知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.13,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,仍然有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.92,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,详细 不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:10.73,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 道具？为了收集遗体？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:13.49,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,你觉得是就是咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:18.12,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,少云里雾里胡扯了 有事快说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:20.57,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,是遗体情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.77,0:04:25.96,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,哈尔特根公国 史蒂芬·哈尔特根公王拥有遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.74,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不巧这情报我早有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:31.53,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,正打算明天去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:32.96,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.63,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,但是这次没那么简单哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:37.38,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:40.01,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,从这里算 乘机车要一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:43.25,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,小心被其他嘉依卡抢了先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:48.12,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不爽 不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.28,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这小子究竟是谁的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:54.49,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,听那口气 他也向红嘉依卡提供了情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆 让红嘉依卡去抢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.69,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这招也行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.66,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,奇伊那小子 为什么知道妮娃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,贝 想要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:07.62,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,贝？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:11.59,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.05,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,吃太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这都吃多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:15.08,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:17.73,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,连壳都吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:20.43,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,这玩意能当铠甲材料啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:22.49,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,贝想要 紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.72,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,烹调中 稍微待机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:30.56,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,真够惨的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.57,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,普通战斗 不会弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.36,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,魔法 攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:40.32,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,而且是 有相当实力的魔法师 或者强力的机枪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:45.12,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,这座塔 构造也跟魔法有关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:47.79,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,究竟发生了什么 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.75,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,卡莲小姐在书库中找到的资料中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:55.93,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,藏匿皇帝遗产的研究所 会不会就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.76,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,那么 所谓的遗产究竟在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:04.05,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,什么人 给我老实出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:09.14,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,你们来这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:12.44,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,我们是 六国联合下属
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,克里曼机关 基列特队的队员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:16.44,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,六国联合？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.36,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,你们俩 是贾兹帝国的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.61,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,是又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:23.57,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,知道了 到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:26.56,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,战争已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.83,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,我们在这打毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:31.21,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,而且也不是来抓你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:36.49,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,这里发生了什么 能说明一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:42.34,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,来了叫嘉依卡的 一红一白两个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.57,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,和你一样的瞳色和发色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:46.91,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,我们不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.85,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,然后呢 她们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:55.82,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,白色嘉依卡走近后 伊茨玛希制造的人偶突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,变成机枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:04.24,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,果然 这座岛是贾兹皇帝的秘密研究所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:10.41,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,亚人兵和弃兽的量产 以及操纵它们的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.92,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,除了战争还能怎么用？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:19.38,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,为什么这个伊茨玛希 即使皇帝死了 还在继续研究
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.47,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,好像是皇帝的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:25.39,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,即便自己死了 也肯定会用到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:27.64,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,是嘉依卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:32.10,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,所以 嘉依卡·贾兹在这来之不易的太平盛世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:35.15,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,是能再次引发战乱的灾厄之种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:39.09,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,果然不能让嘉依卡收集遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.36,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,所以是嘉依卡带走了机仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.99,Default,Ursula,0,0,0,,嗯 是人偶跟着嘉依卡走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:48.66,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,问够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.07,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,你们要留在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:56.13,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,不想回去 因为大陆上无处容身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.45,Default,Cyril,0,0,0,,我们俩的事 别再多管了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:08.25,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,可以推定嘉依卡带走的机枪就是皇帝遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.35,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,既然落到女儿嘉依卡手中…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:16.00,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,机枪使用皇帝遗体成为强大武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:20.32,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,能让这世界再次陷入混乱…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:24.06,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,嗯 但绝不能让它发生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.68,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,嗯？猫头鹰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:35.65,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,传命基列特队 火速前往哈尔特根公国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:41.50,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,八英雄之一 哈尔特根正召集军士 有增强军备之嫌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.34,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,火速前往调查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,上面这样写
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:49.01,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,既然是英雄之一 嘉依卡也会冲着遗体去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:51.88,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,嗯 我们去哈尔特根公国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.10,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:01.18,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,收集遗体的目的 为了凭悼父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.68,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,但是 我 孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:05.97,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,并非贾兹皇帝女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.76,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 十分清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:12.08,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,但是 想收集之情 无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.04,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:18.39,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,现在收集遗体还有什么用 你会迷茫我理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:21.94,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,但是没关系 我决心已定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:27.75,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,虽然不知道集齐后会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.39,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,但是 你做到满意为止就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:34.42,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我决定奉陪到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:36.54,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.25,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,我回来了 兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.80,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,抓到了很多软体动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.47,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,虽然味道不明 但不是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.43,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,切大块加点酸味应该不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:57.08,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,还抓到了兄长想要的软体动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.90,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我可没想要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.55,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,放我头上干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:03.86,Default,Akari,10,10,0,,放头上更有男人味怎么就是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:02.65,OPEDEG,Toru,0,0,0,,喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.41,Default,David,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.26,Default,David,0,0,0,,不是吧 这就开始了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.63,Default,David,0,0,0,,看来城墙内侧整个都是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:25.01,Default,Red,0,0,0,,迅速地 打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.97,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,Sadica, asdic, rimazo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.35,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,守御阻拒之物显现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.53,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,预选通过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:49.78,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,武艺大会要两人 或三人一组作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:53.88,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,关于武器 只要课携带就不做限制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:57.04,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,武器和防具可随意使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.50,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,当然也包括机枪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.26,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,你们是三人一组吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:01.84,Default,David,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.97,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,那就把布绑胳膊上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.01,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,以证明参加大会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:09.69,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,然后去第二城墙内的兵营
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.64,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,哈尔特根公王陛下 只要真正的<武>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:18.66,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,所以这名为大会 实为以命相搏的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:20.06,Default,Red,0,0,0,,早已知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.17,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,简直像战争
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:24.54,Default,David,0,0,0,,喔？要弃权吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:25.40,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.87,Default,David,0,0,0,,正式站是明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:30.39,Default,David,0,0,0,,看来只能在兵营歇着了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.77,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,伤还痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:33.95,Default,David,0,0,0,,不算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.79,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,大卫 勉强 不可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.64,Default,David,0,0,0,,喂喂喂 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:42.42,Default,David,0,0,0,,你突然冒出句温柔话来倒让我担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:47.19,Default,David,0,0,0,,与其担心我 还是先顾自己的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:53.01,Default,David,0,0,0,,拿到奖品遗体后 还要把白丫头的全抢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.79,Default,David,0,0,0,,当然 如今还问 愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.79,Default,David,0,0,0,,那就打起精神来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.44,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,白色手中的遗体 大会的奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:04.94,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,全部夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.24,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,大会之前灭了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.92,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,来试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:20.06,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,你们俩 还不住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.75,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,再不停手 就禁止你们出赛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:36.83,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,收拾干净
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:38.46,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,他是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:39.88,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,你不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:42.94,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,因身手不凡 公王赏识之下雇来的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.04,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,可也不至于杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:53.61,Default,Owner,0,0,0,,虽说叫武艺大会 但那只是互相厮杀罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:54.95,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,互相厮杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:55.73,Default,Owner,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:59.88,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,但是 参加者以命相搏 有意义么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:03.12,Default,Owner,0,0,0,,这个…因为赢了就有钱和地位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:07.21,Default,Owner,0,0,0,,优胜者能成为骑士 被召入城内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:12.93,Default,Owner,0,0,0,,还能得到公王在讨伐贾兹皇帝时缴来的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.10,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,宝贝？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.43,Default,Owner,0,0,0,,听我句劝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.79,Default,Owner,0,0,0,,大会结束之前 最好别接近那城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:25.85,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,确实如奇伊所说 这次不简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:32.53,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,原本哈尔特根公国 就奖励国民习武
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:37.89,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,公王凯旋之后 大会突然变这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:40.77,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,参加者开始不断进入城内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.94,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,为什么要厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.04,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,我不觉得这正常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.26,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:51.83,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,好 马特乌和芷依塔去求见哈尔特根公王 探探情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.47,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,我和薇薇装成参加者 混入大会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.22,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,李奥纳多去查查参加者的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:03.25,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Aida, fual, alluel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.68,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,显现吧 包裹隐藏之物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.85,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,<隐蔽者>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.86,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,OK 完美的隐蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:18.84,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,格伦森城 城墙 极其高大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.11,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,潜入 困难？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:23.20,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,是啊 只能正面上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.41,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,参加武艺大会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.54,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,我也可以参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.05,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 芙蕾多妮卡 援助 请求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:33.42,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.13,Default,chaika,0,0,0,,大闹 非常 赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.31,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:40.68,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄长 借装铠龙的力量 我看可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:41.51,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:45.02,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,城墙内 进入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:46.78,Default,Navi,0,0,0,,探索 需要？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:50.64,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 探索 夺取遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.33,Default,Navi,0,0,0,,夺取完成 同时任务完成？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:56.68,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 然后 找机会逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.15,Default,Navi,0,0,0,,尽早 需要调查遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.44,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 妮娃 聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.49,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,聪明？预料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.20,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,妮娃 谦虚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:07.87,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,谦虚 有实力者 限制专用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.29,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,所以 这是谦虚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:11.63,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,妮娃 愉快 好人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.38,Default,Niva,0,0,0,,不是人 我 机枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.59,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,差别无多 妮娃 人格 有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:39.70,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,哈尔特根公王陛下 能有幸面见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:43.20,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,我是克里曼机关副队长 马特乌斯·卡拉威
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.31,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:48.34,Default,Hartgen,0,0,0,,若是武艺大会 我无意中止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.37,Default,Hartgen,0,0,0,,顺便一提 也无意归还遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:56.71,Default,Hartgen,0,0,0,,如何 你们要不要一同观战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:04.22,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,喂喂 这些家伙可是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.56,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,你太温柔了 尼克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.45,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.39,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,根本不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.62,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.01,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,已经开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:31.54,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:35.42,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不好意思 我们要参加武艺大会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:42.88,Default,Both,0,0,0,,去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:49.22,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,显现吧 冲击粉碎之物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.27,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,<重击者>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:57.19,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,打倒 成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:00.99,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,这就完了？没我出场机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:02.49,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 最强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现阶段 温存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.91,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,诶 这算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:07.42,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,预选通过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这个绑胳膊上 是参加者的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.62,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,那女孩是谁？观战的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.33,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.21,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,哟 有精神就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.23,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:40.15,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,瞧这招呼 明明是我救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.66,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:44.86,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,是吗 忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:49.16,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,我能看穿哦 你心中的那份憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.91,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,所以我救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:26.95,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,你该早就发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:32.99,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,在这没有战争的世界中 总有一丝朦胧的违和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:38.80,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,心中如漩涡般充斥着 对世界的不满和疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:43.74,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,这些 证明你无法活在这个太平之世上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:47.07,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,所以你拔了剑 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:53.23,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,向那意欲牺牲自己宝贵部下的 只有高傲自满的正义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:55.98,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,然后想要杀死对方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.13,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:58.90,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,为王工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:02.43,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,什么意思 你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.12,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,你会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:15.20,Default,Red,0,0,0,,白嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:16.41,Default,Red,0,0,0,,这次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:20.27,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,嘉依卡肯定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:23.31,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:45.30,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,尼克拉队长和薇薇 按计划混入参加者中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.28,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,黑嘉依卡的事也已通知到位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:52.58,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,另外会场内 有白嘉依卡和红嘉依卡的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.18,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,看来 是要参加大会
